# Project Overview: Bright Coffee Shop Sales Analysis

This project analyzes transactional sales data from Bright Coffee Shop to generate valuable business insights that support strategic decision-making.
The dataset covers six months of daily sales activity, offering detailed information on product performance, customer purchasing behavior, and revenue trends.

The main objective is to help the newly appointed CEO understand the key factors driving business performance and identify opportunities for growth.
Using data analytics, SQL, and visualization techniques, the project transforms raw sales data into actionable insights.

The analysis focuses on identifying top-performing products, determining peak business hours, and uncovering sales trends across different time periods.
It also evaluates overall store performance and provides data-driven recommendations aimed at increasing sales, improving operational efficiency, and enhancing profitability.


The findings from this project will support informed business decisions and strategic planning for Bright Coffee Shop.
